[6.133787, "o", "\u001b[1mSieve demo\u001b[0m — \u001b[1;36m6\u001b[0m messages through the proxy:\r\n\r\n"]
[6.133979, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m1\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mHi, I'm Casey. I work as a landscape architect.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.571991, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m Hello Casey! Nice to meet you. Landscape architecture is a fascinating field—blending art, design, and ecology to shape our outdoor spaces. Is there anything specific you'd like help with, whether it's planning a project, \r\nresearch, or anyth  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall rounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m0\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m4352884\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.572101, "o", "\r\n"]
[10.572417, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m2\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mMy favourite project so far is the riverside park in Bristol.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.446696, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m That sounds great! Bristol's riverside park is a fantastic project. Is this one you're working on currently, or something from your portfolio?  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall rounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m0\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m7818573\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.446787, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.447024, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m3\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mI have a dog called Mabel, she's a border terrier.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[31.723311, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m That's wonderful, Casey! Mabel sounds like a great companion—Border Terriers are known for being tough, friendly, and full of character. Is she well-behaved, and does she enjoy spending time in the gardens with you?  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mrounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m1\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m13211461\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[31.723693, "o", "\r\n"]
[31.724022, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m4\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mDo you remember where I work?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[38.968897, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m Yes, I remember you work as a landscape architect.  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall rounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m0\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m7182764\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[38.969045, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m5\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mWhat breed is Mabel?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[45.300338, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m Mabel is a border terrier.\r\n\u001b[1m<\u001b[0m\u001b[35m/\u001b[0m\u001b[95mthink\u001b[0m\u001b[1m>\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nBased on your memory, Mabel is a border terrier.  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall rounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m0\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m6268357\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[45.300468, "o", "\r\n"]
[45.300701, "o", "\u001b[2mturn \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m6\u001b[0m\u001b[2m:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mDo you remember where Pat works?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[47.139482, "o", "        \u001b[32m→\u001b[0m I don't have any information about where Pat works. We haven't stored any details about someone named Pat.  \u001b[1;2m(\u001b[0m\u001b[2mrecall rounds: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m1\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, proxy_us: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;36m1779094\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[47.139697, "o", "\u001b[2mCheck \u001b[0m\u001b[2;36msieve status\u001b[0m\u001b[2m to see how many facts Sieve learned.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
